    "body": "### Problem\n\nhours ago while inputting `()`, i noticed the cursor was gone for a short time. i managed to know that's [&showmatch](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/master/src/nvim/search.c#L2320), who hijacks the cursor for &matchtime at most, changes cursor position and cursor shape, which i think is an intrusive design, also distracts user.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nas we have extmark now, i believe the impl of &showmatch can be evolved.",
